Boxcar Conductor
==============

This plugin provides you with deployment tools for your Rails application, which 
will help you deploy to your RailsBoxcar.com instance.

Usage

./script/plugin install git://github.com/robbyrussell/boxcar-conductor.git

# Configure your Boxcar 
cap boxcar:config

# Deploy!
cap deploy


Feature Requests / Bugs

* http://planetargon.lighthouseapp.com/projects/9962-boxcar-conductor

